headline: 4 Consumer Product Stocks Gaining Attention Amid Industry Momentum
summary: The Zacks Consumer Products - Staples industry participants thrive on innovation and digital growth, catering to evolving consumer preferences. Solid saving efforts keep KMB, CLX, ACI and OLLI well-placed amid cost challenges.
